        {
            "title": "華為被發現在頂級AI晶片中採用了台積電、三星和SK海力士的組件",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 一家研究機構在拆解過程中發現，華為至少在其部分昇騰(Ascend)人工智能晶片中採用了亞洲最大科技企業的先進組件，這凸顯出中國在努力提升本土人工智能半導體生產的同時仍依賴海外硬體。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">TechInsights在聲明中稱，其在多款華為Ascend 910C晶片樣本中發現了台積電、三星電子和SK海力士的元件。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家總部位於渥太華的研究機構在調查中認定，華為加速器所用的晶片裸片由台積電製造。他們還發現了一種由三星和SK海力士生產的較老一代高帶寬內存HBM2E。TechInsights表示，在兩份不同的Ascend 910C樣本中都發現了這兩家製造商的組件。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-250673aa-89e3-38d0-80ea-5636e18168fc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在中國正值為期一周的假期期間，華為未回應置評請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Huawei Used TSMC, Samsung, SK Hynix Components in Top AI Chips</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Yoolim Lee、Yuan Gao、Debby Wu、Peter Elstrom.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%A2%AB%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%9C%A8%E9%A0%82%E7%B4%9Aai%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E4%B8%AD%E6%8E%A1%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%86%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB-%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%92%8Csk%E6%B5%B7%E5%8A%9B%E5%A3%AB%E7%9A%84%E7%B5%84%E4%BB%B6-085601379.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-03 17:25:42",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
